Description: Visual tool for ROS2 development
 ROS Weaver is a visual tool for assembling, extending, and iterating
 on ROS2 packages and nodes. Features include:
  - Visual node graph editor with drag-and-drop
  - Live system introspection and monitoring
  - Code generation for packages and launch files
  - Rosbag recording and playback
  - AI-powered architecture assistance
  - Mission planning with waypoint editor
